item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Account_ProofOfConcept_Review_History
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Account_ProofOfConcept_Review_History Datatype Description Summary of review activity for a proof of concept request. Local accountCreatedFlag True for approved requests associated with a new account and false otherwise. Type: boolean deniedFlag True for denied requests and false otherwise. Type: boolean events List of events occurring during the review. Type: SoftLayer_Container_Account_ProofOfConcept_Review_Event[] reviewCompleteFlag True for fully reviewed requests and false otherwise.
